Gui, Add, Button, %k_Position%, 9

Gui, Add, Button, %k_Position%, A
Gui, Add, Button, %k_Position%, B
Gui, Add, Button, %k_Position%, C
Gui, Add, Button, %k_Position%, D
Gui, Add, Button, %k_Position%, E
Gui, Add, Button, %k_Position%, F
