Gui, Add, Button, %k_Position%, H
Gui, Add, Button, %k_Position%, I
Gui, Add, Button, %k_Position%, J
Gui, Add, Button, %k_Position%, K
Gui, Add, Button, %k_Position%, L
Gui, Add, Button, %k_Position%, M
